archimate:DataObject.name: Private Data
archimate:DataObject.documentation: Data over which an Entity exerts access control. In Sovrin Infrastructure, Private Data is never stored on the Sovrin Ledger. Private Data may be stored by an Agent in a Wallet or Vault or other secure location. Mutually exclusive with Public Data.
